  - Load exif data
  - DirectX10/11 support for ILUT?
  - Make PSD loader handle layers correctly
  - ILU selection (extension of region)
    - iluCopySelection()
  - some kind of iluMixSlices (eg. convert FITS to colour)?
  - vector formats (svg)
  - eps
  - camera raw formats (dng, .nef, .crw, .orf ...)
